quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Ha, Miiym. (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo zose n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  43,2,Ndarahiye kuri iki gitabu gitagatifu kimenyesha neza aya majambo
  43,3,Ntankeka natwe twagize ngo kibe igisomwa co mururimi rw’icarabu kugira ngo mutegere neza
  43,4,Mu vy’ukuri iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu iri mububiko bw’ibitabu vyose vyavuye iwacu kandi n’igitabu catewe iteka n’ubuhizi
  43,5,Mbega natwe tureke kubibutsa kubera yuko mwabaye abantu mwamaze kurengerana kumabi yanyu
  43,6,Mu bantu bakera twebwe twaraba rungikiye intumwa z’Imana nyinshi
  43,7,Ntantumwa y’Imana iyariyo yose atari uko bahora bayigaya nukuyityoza
  43,8,Rero twaraba honeje abari bafise ubushobozi buhanitse gusumba abo baqurayshi hamwe n’uburorero bw’ibihano vyashikiye abantu baho hambere
  43,9,"Ubabajije uti:- mbega ni nde yaremye Amajuru n’Isi? Mu vy’ukuri bakwishura bati :- uwaremye ibi vyose n’uwufise ubushobozi hamwe n’ubumenyi"
  43,10,Uwabagiriye iy’Isi kuba nk’ubusaswa nukugira amayira muriyo nukugira ngo murongore iyo mugomba kuja ahariho hose
  43,11,Nuwamanuye amazi avuye mubicu kurugero no kuri ayo mazi niho twazuye Isi yari yarapfuye nikuri ivyo niko muzozurwa
  43,12,Uwaremye ikigabo n’ikigore mubintu vyose nukubagirira amato hamwe n’ibikoko mwurira ko
  43,13,"Kugira ngo mwicareko neza hejuru y’imigongo yavyo hanyuma mwibuke imigisha y’Umuremyi wanyu mugihe mwicaye neza hejuru yavyo muvuga muti :- nihaninahazwe Imana yatugamburukije ibi vyose kandi ntitwari kwigirira ibi vyose"
  43,14,Ntankeka twebwe tuzo subira ku Muremyi wacu
  43,15,Bamugirira mubantu beranda ahantu bavuga yuko ibi biremwa ari ibibondo vy’Imana mu vy’ukuri umuntu n’umuhakanyi w’imihezagiro iri k’umugaragaro
  43,16,Yitwariye ibibondo vy’abakobwa muvyo yiremeye mukubatorera mwebwe ibibondo vy’abahungu
  43,17,"Umwe muribo mugihe ashikirijwe inkuru y’ivyo yagiriweko akarorero kanyene imigisha, mumaso yiwe haca hirabura cane n’agahinda kenshi"
  43,18,Uwarerewe mubisharizo nawe kubijanye nibihari ntashobora kuvuga k’umugaragaro
  43,19,"Kandi bagira Abamarayika aribo biremwa vy’Imana vyeranda ngo n’abagore bayo, mbega n’ivyabona mukuremwa kwabo? Ukuba kwabo kw’ivyabona kuzo kwandikwa kandi bazobazwa"
  43,20,"Bavuga bati:- iyo ishaka nyene imigisha mininiya ntitwari kubasenga, kuko atabumenyi bafise kuri ibi vyose kandi ntibavuga atari amajambo y’ububeshi bw’ivyo bavuze"
  43,21,Mbega twebwe ntitwabahaye igitabu imbere y’iki ? Nabo bakaba bagifashe nkankama
  43,22,"Ahubwo bavuga bati :- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twasanze abavyeyi bacu kubera imigenzo yabo natwe twaciye dukurikira nkuko bamye bagira"
  43,23,"Kandi ntitwarungitse uwutuza mubisagara ivyarivyo vyose atari uko abatunzi baho bavuze bati:- mu vy’ukuri twebwe twasanze abavyeyi bacu n’imigenzo yabo natwe duca dukurikiza ingeso zabo"
  43,24,"Yavuze ati:- naho ndabazaniye imigenzo yacu ifise uburokoke bwiza gusumba iyo bari basanganywe abo bavyeyi banyu, nabo baciye bavuga bati:- twebwe turanse ubwo butumwa mwarungikanywe"
  43,25,"Rero natwe duca turabihora, mugabo nimurabe ukugene kwabaye amaherezo yabigize abahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri"
  43,26,"N’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii) mugihe yabwira umuvyeyi wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- ntankeka jewe mbanje kuba kure yivyo mwebwe musenga"
  43,27,Dukuye mwo gusa uwandemye mu vy’ukuri niwe azondongora
  43,28,Ninawe yagize iri jambo rizo gumaho muruvyaro rwiwe kugira ngo bagaruke
  43,29,Ahubwo baranezerejwe mugihe bari kumwe n’abavyeyi babo kugeza naho bashikirwa n’ukuri n’intumwa y’Imana irabi garagaza
  43,30,"Mugihe bashikirwa n’ukuri baciye bavuga bati:- ubu n’uburozi kandi mu vy’ukuri twebwe turabu hakanye"
  43,31,"Nabo bavuze bati:- ni kuki iyi Qur’aani itamanuwe k’umuntu mukuru wo muri ibi bisagara vyacu bibiri bikuru bikuru"
  43,32,"Mbega nibo bagabura imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe, twebwe twarabugabuye ubu buzima bwabo ku buzima bwo ng’aha kw’Isi, kandi twarabareruye bamwe muribo tubaha n’iteka rininiya cane gusumba abandi, kuri ivyo rero bamwe muribo bagira abandi kuba ari abakozi babo, n’imigisha y’Umuremyi wawe niyo myiza gusumba ivyo begeranya"
  43,33,"Iyo hataba abantu kuba ari umurwi umwe, ntankeka twari kugira ibisenge vy’inzu z’abantu bahakana nyene imigisha kuba ari iz’umwakaka hamwe n’ingazi burirako"
  43,34,N’inzugi z’inzu zabo hamwe n’ubusaswa bwabo hamwe n’inyegamo z’ukwegamira ko
  43,35,Ahubwo n’inzahabu mugabo ivyo vyose ntaco bimaze atari amahirwe y’ubuzima bwo ng’aha kw’isi gusa nayo k’umusi w’imperuka uri ku Muremyi wawe niyaba yigamburukira
  43,36,Uwuyagirira ubuhumyi amajambo yanyene imigisha tumushirira ho Shetani kuba ariyo mugenzi wiwe
  43,37,Nabo nabazitira inzira y’amahirwe bakiyumvira yuko barokotse
  43,38,"N’igihe azodushikira k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi nawe atwarwa mumuriro udahera azovuga abwira Shetani ati:- iyo aba ari kure y’ubuseruko n’ubumanuko hagati yanje na wewe, n’ubugenzi bubi bumeze gute"
  43,39,Uno musi nta nakimwe kizoba marira muvyo mwahemukiye imitima yanyu yuko mwebwe muri kumwe mubijanye n’ibihano
  43,40,"Mbega woshobora kwumvisha abatumva, canke woshobora kurongora impumyi hamwe n’abari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  43,41,Twebwe nitwagukura ng’aha kw’isi utarabona ibihano vyabo ntugire amakenga twebwe tuzokwihora kuribo
  43,42,"Canke twebwe tuzokwereka neza muvyo twasezeranye nabo, natwe ntankeka turafise ububasha buri hejuru yabo"
  43,43,"Rero nubifate nka nkama kuvyo twaguhaye, kandi ntankeka wewe uri munzira nziza igororotse"
  43,44,"Mu vy’ukuri iki n’icibutso kuri wewe no ku bantu bawe, n’ubu vuba mwese muzobazwa"
  43,45,"Nimugende mubaze intumwa zacu twazanye imbere yawe, mbega twebwe twoba twaragize izindi Mana zisengwa aho gusenga nyene imigisha myinshi ihagije"
  43,46,"Ntankeka twebwe twararungitse intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ifise amajambo yacu iyajana kwa Fir’auni no kubakuru b’abantu babo nukubabwira iti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nd’intumwa y’Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  43,47,"Mugabo mugihe yashika afise ivyemezo vyacu, mu mwanya baciye bazitwenga ntibazemera"
  43,48,Kandi ntitwaberetse icemezo icarico cose atari icemezo cari kininiya gusumba ica mugenzi wiwe nukuba fata kubihano vyacu kugira ngo bagaruke iwacu
  43,49,"Nabo bavuze bati:- wamurozi we ! dusabire ku Muremyi wawe kubijanye naya ndagano yaguhaye mu vy’ukuri tuzoba turi mu bantu barongotse"
  43,50,Rero mugihe twaba kuriraho ivyo bihano mukanya isase twaciye tubona bayahonyanga ko
  43,51,"Nuyo Fir’auni yara menyesheje ku bantu biwe avuga ati:- bantu banje intwaro y’igihugu ca Misiri si rwanje hamwe n’izi nzuzi zica imbere yanje, mbega ntavyo mubona"
  43,52,"Canke jewe ntacomaze gusumba uyu Mussa ajunjagariye ng’aha, kandi adashoboye kuvuga ibintu bitomoye"
  43,53,"Mbega ni kuki atambitswe ibisharizo vy’inzahabu, canke ngo haze abamarayika bari kumwe nawe bamu kurikira"
  43,54,"Yasanze bagaba nukiwe n’ubwenge bamu gamburukira, mugihe bari mu bantu bataye umurongo"
  43,55,"Rero mugihe badu shavuza, twaciye tubihora, duca tubibiza mumazi uko bangana bose"
  43,56,Hanyuma twaciye tubagira kuba akarorero n’ibiganiro ku bantu bazoba baje munyuma yabo
  43,57,No mugihe yaciribwa ko akarorero umwana wa Mariyamu (iii) mumwanya abantu bawe baciye bakoma akaruru
  43,58,"Baca bavuga bati:- mbega Imana zacu nizo nziza gusumba canke niwe, canke ntaco bakubwira atari munzira z’ibihari gusa, ahubwo abo bantu n’abasinzi"
  43,59,Ntiyari intumwa y’Imana ariwe Issa mwene Mariyamu (iii) atari uko yari umushumvyi w’Imana twamanuriye nuku mugira umwe muburorero bwiza kuri bene Israeri
  43,60,Iyo tuba dushaka twari kubagira Abamarayika bari ngaha kw’Isi aho kuba ari mwebwe kuri iy’Isi
  43,61,Mu vy’ukuri n’ikimenyetso c’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi kandi ntimukigirire amakenga kandi nimunkurikire iyi niyo nzira igororotse
  43,62,"Kandi Shetani ntibazitire, ntankeka kuri mwebwe niwe mwansi wanyu, kandi niwe mwansi wanyu aboneka neza k’umugaragaro"
  43,63,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Issa mwene Mariamu (iii) yari afise ibimenyetso biri k’umugaragaro yavuze ati :- ndabashikiye mfise ubumenyi kugira ngo ndaba menyeshe bimwe muvyo mutumvikanyeko, rero ni mutinye Imana nanje mungamburukire"
  43,64,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana niyo Muremyi wanje kandi niyo Muremyi wanje n’Umuremyi wanyu, rero ni muyisenge kuko niyo nzira igororotse"
  43,65,Imirwi n’iyindi yaracanye mwo rero bazoshikirwa bamwe bahemukiye imitima yabo muguhonywa n’ibihano vy’umusi ubabaza cane
  43,66,Barindiriye iki atari ugushikirwa n’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi gusa kandi ukazoba shikira giturumbuka nabo aho bari batabizi
  43,67,Abagenzi kuri uwo musi bazoba bari abansi kubandi dukuye mwo b’abagenzi bamye bagamburukira Imana yabo y’ukuri
  43,68,Bantu banje ntabwoba muzoba mufise kuri uwo musi w’imperuka kandi mwebwe ntimuzo teterwa
  43,69,Abemeye amajambo yacu bakaba bari aba Isilamu b’ukuri
  43,70,"Nimwinjire mumirima yo mw’ijuru mwebwe n’imiryango yanyu, iyo niho muzo nezerezwa"
  43,71,Bazohora bacishirizwa amasahani y’inzahabu hamwe n’ibikombe vyabo birimwo ivyo imitima yabo yipfuza hamwe n’ivyo amaso yabo azonezereza namwe iyo mw’Ijuru muzobayo mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  43,72,N’uwu n’umurima mwasigiwe kuvyo mwahora mugira
  43,73,Murahafitiye ivyamwa vyinshi muzo fungurira yo
  43,74,Mu vy’ukuri abahakanyi b’Imana bazoba bicaye mubihano vyo mumuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu
  43,75,"Ntibazo ruhutswa nivyo bihano biri muri uwo muriro udahera, kandi niho bazo kwiheburira yo"
  43,76,"Natwe ntitwaba hemukiye, ahubwo nibo bonyene bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  43,77,"Kandi bazokoma induru bavuga bati:- ewe mwami wacu, uyo Muremyi wawe natwice, nawe ace abishura ati :- ntankeka mwebwe aho muri muzoguma muri uwo muriro nyene"
  43,78,Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twarakuzaniye ukuri kwama mugabo benshi muri mwebwe mwamye mukugaya uko kuri kwama
  43,79,"Egome,\tboshobora\tgucishaho\titegeko,\tcanke\tnatwe\tturashobora gucishaho irindi"
  43,80,"Canke\tbikeka\tyuko\ttwebwe\ttutumva\tamabanga\tyabo\thamwe n’ukwongorerana kwabo, oya ! n’intumwa zacu ziri hafi yabo baravyandika"
  43,81,"Vuga uti:- nyene imigisha iyo iba ifise ikibondo nari kuba uwambere mukuyisenga"
  43,82,Umuremyi w’Amujuru n’Isi Umuremyi n’inyegamo yiwe ntagatifu iri kure nivyo bayihayagiza ko
  43,83,Rero nimubareke bagume bayogora nugutamba batarika kugeza naho bazohura n’uwo musi wabo baraganiwe
  43,84,"Niyo isengwa mw’Ijuru no kw’Isi, nayo niyo nyene ubuhizi n’ubumenyi buhagiije"
  43,85,"Niyo iterwa iteka ry’ukuri kuko ariwe mwami w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe n’ibirimwo vyose nirwiwe, kandi irafise ubumenyi bw’ugushika k’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi, namwe uko muri kwose muzo subizwa iwe"
  43,86,Nabo ntabubasha bafise bw’ugu sabira abo basabira atari Imana yonyene dukuye mwo bamwe bemera uku kuri nukuyimenya
  43,87,"Ubabajije uti;- ni nde yabaremye? Mu vy’ukuri bakwishura bati:- n’Imana, none ni hehe bahindukirizwa"
  43,88,"N’imvugo yiwe n’iyi:- ewe Muremyi wanje, mu vy’ukuri aba n’abantu batemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  43,89,Rero nubagirire ikigongwe kandi ubabwire amajambo y’amahoro kuko ubu vuba bazotegera neza